   - Authorized security assessments of your own systems
   - Legitimate security research with proper authorization
   - Testing applications and networks that you own or have written permission to test

4. COMPLIANCE RESPONSIBILITY: Users are solely responsible for ensuring their use
   of this software complies with all applicable local, state, national, and
